parameters: Umi "I can fight! I will protect Mia!"
Kru "Is that so! Then I'll protect you both!"
Umi "Mia! I'm so glad... you're safe!"
Kru "That's great. You can relax now."
Umi "Mia doesn't usually take to people. This is a first."
Kru "Really? Doesn't seem like it though."
Kru "What's with that stare? Is there something on my face?"

Kru "But seriously, why were you being attacked by a monster? You don't
look tasty enough to eat."
Ah... so this is how I die...
That girl... Umi... was that her name...
